{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99708-fa-di-he-qing-she","title":"法蒂和青蛇","description":"对法蒂，一名非常努力完成她所被交代的事的小女孩来说，每天都是一个新的开始。 在这个故事中，法蒂与父亲一起收集木柴时受到惊讶。法蒂和绿蛇是基于在加纳北部长大的女孩的真实冒险经历。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Therson  Boadu"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99708-fa-di-he-qing-she"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62460/size3/731db424da42564f209ccf9e5c96a6c4.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62460/size6/731db424da42564f209ccf9e5c96a6c4.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62461/size6/1420940c8a6a76ef5cb23d5eecdcfd83.jpg","text":"法蒂是个小女孩像风一样奔跑，喜欢笑，也尽量去做别人交代她的事。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62462/size6/a409a7aa004d9c412a25281b94db86ef.jpg","text":"有一天，法蒂和她的母亲和父亲去寻找柴火。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62463/size6/1f0440c0fabf1359fbfcac1fb2414a72.jpg","text":"法蒂很想帮助她的母亲和父亲，但有这么多事可做，有这么多东西要看：鸟儿，猴子，天空！","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62464/size6/087a16d3f15ffcac981fef49908fccef.jpg","text":"妈妈说，“法蒂！ 请听话！ 你可以在这里找到柴火，也可以在那里寻找柴火......","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62465/size6/390ec5c56c3bbd6201631435c25dbb38.jpg","text":"...但是法蒂， 请注意看你去哪里而小心安全。“\n她说，“是的，妈妈。”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62466/size6/61bec54eab6a97e2ff55702078c1f5e6.jpg","text":"不久之后，她的母亲和父亲开始忙碌。","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62467/size6/4e8fb6cc85b4df264c40b760ac84666d.jpg","text":"他们找到了大块的木柴。\n他们找到了一些小块的木柴。","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62468/size6/d7df140cd7c43e8ff6b6aeabeff321ee.jpg","text":"法蒂也很忙。\n她找到了一些小块的木柴。\n她找到了一些非常小块的木柴。","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62469/size6/f07993104a68c6ce37717f151f51f851.jpg","text":"那时法蒂抬头看了看。\n看到了一只红色的小鸟\n在高高的草丛中。","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62470/size6/2a6ce22d25daf28416f5247f069c3e7c.jpg","text":"接着，法蒂低下头看了看。 看到了一只棕色的蚂蚁在尘土飞扬的小路上。","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62471/size6/18b03a3e6a83a1ef0208c70280e41b21.jpg","text":"后来法蒂看到了一片美丽的叶子。 叶子又光滑又绿。 她把一根手指放在美丽的叶子上。","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62472/size6/9363b4c68b636fc4660389d9c4ffb035.jpg","text":"法蒂说：“这个感觉上不像是一片叶子。\n”\n美丽的叶子突然动了一下！\n法蒂说：“这并不是一片美丽的叶子。 这是一条青蛇！\n”","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62473/size6/a1f48fc5e458c917e8c87e8e83fb6dfe.jpg","text":"“啊！”，法蒂尖叫着。法蒂跑得很快，去找她的母亲和父亲。","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62474/size6/2e873546578bacea6f721d2ea59bc36a.jpg","text":"法蒂看到了她的父亲。 法蒂说：“一条蛇！ 一条蛇！”\n父亲说，“在哪里？ 哪里？”\n法蒂说：“那里！ 在那里！”","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62475/size6/340a6d2f7c774cb8c063b2d2f361a5a3.jpg","text":"她的父亲用了一把棍子追赶那只青蛇。\n青蛇溜走了。","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62476/size6/32f02796b479b933a5ed4c95ba957a42.jpg","text":"父亲说：“法蒂，你现在安全了。 我们去找妈妈告诉她青蛇的事。”","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62477/size6/48f3ece8593679fbc7532f276f8c649a.jpg","text":"妈妈说，“法蒂，我很高兴青蛇没咬你...","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/62478/size6/c26b9d5f5c67ee1cb073fde9e35efd76.jpg","text":"......但下次请拜托，看看你去哪里，小心安全。\n”\n 那事就这么结束了。","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":18,"words":45}}